{
  "text": "The authors acknowledge that the speci\u02c6city of chemical inhibitors to canine cytochrome P450 is limited. Canine CYP1A catalyzes phenacetin O-deethylation. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] The activity is inhibited by furafylline. [CITATION_3] ) Also, canine CYP1A catalyzes ethoxyresoru\u02c6n O-deethylation, [CITATION_4] and the activity is inhibited by both a-naphtho\u2030avone and furafylline.",
  "correct_citation": {
